description:
Today I'm showing you how to make fudgesicles. These vegan fudgesicles take only 5 minutes to make these vegan fudge popsicles but the results are amazing! These are so much more than just frozen chocolate milk, there is a secret ingredient which makes these chocolate popsicles have that chewy, fudgey texture. The best chocolate popsicle recipe out there!
